<!-- PROJECTS -->
<section id="projects" class="section-wrap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="proj-hdr">
      <div class="rv"><div class="eyebrow gold">Signature Innovations</div><h2 class="stitle">Pioneering<br><em>Firsts</em></h2></div>
      <p class="rv d2" style="font-size:.95rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.85;color:rgba(255,255,255,.58);">Two industry-first deployments that set new benchmarks for measurement accuracy and AEP optimisation across Asia — plus an ongoing 1+ GW multi-continent procurement programme.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pgrid">
      <div class="pcard rv">
        <span class="pnum">01 · India · 2013–2014</span>
        <span class="pcard-icon">📡</span>
        <h3 class="ptitle">India's First Nacelle-Mounted LiDAR Campaign</h3>
        <p class="pdesc">Pioneered the first-ever nacelle-mounted LiDAR deployment in India at Surajbari Wind Farm (34.5 MW, 20 Vestas turbines). Achieved using up to 440m wind speed measurement, enabling real-time yaw error correction and power curve measurement accuracy.</p>
        <div class="pstats">
          <div><span class="pstat-n">−7.55°</span><span class="pstat-l">Yaw Error Corrected</span></div>
          <div><span class="pstat-n">2.4%</span><span class="pstat-l">AEP Gain</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ptags"><span class="ptag">LiDAR</span><span class="ptag">Vestas V90</span><span class="ptag">Yaw Correction</span><span class="ptag">Power Curve</span><span class="ptag">34.5 MW</span></div>
        <span class="pbadge">First-mover in India</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pcard rv d2">
        <span class="pnum">02 · Thailand · 2014</span>
        <span class="pcard-icon">🌏</span>
        <h3 class="ptitle">Thailand - Ground-Based LiDAR for WRA</h3>
        <p class="pdesc">Designed Thailand's first ground-based LiDAR wind measurement campaign in complex terrain. 4 strategic LiDAR locations with CFD-optimised strategy reduced energy yield uncertainty from 14.87% to 13.19% for a 64 MW project at 120m hub height.</p>
        <div class="pstats">
          <div><span class="pstat-n">1.68%</span><span class="pstat-l">Uncertainty Reduced</span></div>
          <div><span class="pstat-n">64 MW</span><span class="pstat-l">Project Scale</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ptags"><span class="ptag">Ground LiDAR</span><span class="ptag">CFD</span><span class="ptag">Complex Terrain</span><span class="ptag">WRA</span></div>
        <span class="pbadge">Regional benchmark</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pcard pcard--w rv">
        <span class="pnum">03 · Portugal + Japan · Active 2020–Present</span>
        <span class="pcard-icon">🌐</span>
        <h3 class="ptitle">1+ GW Multi-Continent WTG Procurement Programme</h3>
        <p class="pdesc">Managing a dual-market WTG procurement programme simultaneously across Europe and Asia-Pacific. Full procurement lifecycle — competitive ITT issuance, binding proposal evaluation, technical and commercial analysis, TSA negotiation and execution. Supported by 800 MW due diligence portfolio in Portugal.</p>
        <div class="pstats">
          <div><span class="pstat-n">800 MW</span><span class="pstat-l">Portugal</span></div>
          <div><span class="pstat-n">200 MW</span><span class="pstat-l">Japan</span></div>
          <div><span class="pstat-n">800 MW</span><span class="pstat-l">Due Diligence</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ptags"><span class="ptag">WTG Procurement</span><span class="ptag">TSA Negotiation</span><span class="ptag">Due Diligence</span><span class="ptag">Portugal</span><span class="ptag">Japan</span><span class="ptag">Blue Power Partners</span></div>
        <span class="pbadge">Active · Ongoing</span>
