      <p style="font-size:.95rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.85;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-top:1rem;max-width:60ch">Browser-based wind resource assessment tool for Power Curve Verification (PCV) site selection per <strong style="color:var(--mint)">IEC 61400-12-1</strong>. Upload your mast and WTG data to identify the best test configuration, perform terrain assessment, and generate DNV-style measurement sector reports.</p>
